      "role": "user",
      "content": "yo can u help me with a headline for this news batch? i need something that really captures the energy of what's happening out there right now.\n\nhere's the feed:\n- crowds gathering at the courthouse for the 3rd day in a row.\n- many participants carrying signs about racial justice and police reform.\n- local businesses reporting some boarded up windows on main st.\n- police presence increased around the plaza due to sporadic shouting and groups blocking traffic.\n- organizers saying the march is peaceful but the vibe is intense.\n- several arrests made following a skirmish near the intersection of 5th and oak.\n- community leaders calling for calm but also for systemic change.\n\nmake it punchy for a news app.",
